pageContext.claim: “Now that they realize the only Collusion with Russia was done by Crooked Hillary Clinton & the Democrats, Nadler, Schiff and the Dem heads of the Committees have gone stone cold CRAZY. 81 letter sent to innocent people to harass them. They won't get ANYTHING done for our Country!”
pageContext.analysis: There is no evidence of collusion between Russia and Democrats, or Russia and Hillary Clinton. In fact, U.S. intelligence agencies agree that Russia interfered in the 2016 election to help Trump win and there are numerous documented ties and contacts between Russians and members of Trump's campaign. Trump is referring to the fact that Fusion GPS, which assembled a dossier on Trump as part of an assignment for Democrats, relied on a British intelligence agent who used Russian sources for his research. So that's a rather big stretch. Moreover, it was a tip from the Australian government, which notified U.S. authorities about a conversation over drinks between a Trump campaign aide, George Papadopoulos, and an Australian diplomat in May, that set off the counterintelligence probe on Trump's campaign -- not the dossier.
